(125, 'Loxapine 25mg 10caps - لوكسابين', '  Loxapine', 'About loxapinea dibenzazepine derivative, a typical antipsychotic.mechanism of action of loxapineloxapine produce its antipsychotic activity by blocking the post synaptic receptor in the cns.indications for loxapinepsychosesinteractions for loxapinealcohol & other cns depressants: additive cns depression. tcas & antiparkinsonism drugs: anticholinergic effects potentiated. clonidine & methyldopa: hypotensive effect of these drugs inhibited. maois: orthostatic hypotension with maois.', NULL, 1, 8.00, '2020-08-30 10:31:01', '2020-08-30 10:31:01'),
