(517, 'Taminil-n 75mg 10 hard gelatin caps -', '  Oseltamivir', 'About oseltamivirsantiviral,neuraminidase inhibitorsmechanism of action of oseltamivirsoseltamivir is an ethyl ester prodrug requiring ester hydrolysis for conversion to active form oseltamivir carboxylate. oseltamivir is a neuraminidase inhibitor, serving as a competitive inhibitor towards sialic acid, found on the surface proteins of normal host cells. by blocking the activity of the viral neuraminidase (na) enzyme, oseltamivir prevents new viral particles from being released by infected cells.sindications for oseltamivirstreatment and prevention of infections due to influenza a and b viruses.sinteractions for oseltamivirsoseltamivir+probenecid: oseltamivir has its toxicity increased by probenecid.', NULL, 1, 189.00, '2020-08-30 10:34:25', '2020-08-30 10:34:25'),
(518, 'Regimax 120mg 20 caps - رجيماكس', '  Orlistat', 'حول المخدرات orlistatanti - السمنة. مشتق من lipstatin.mechanism من عمل orlistatits الوظيفة الأولية هو منع امتصاص الدهون من النظام الغذائي للإنسان ، وبالتالي تقليل السعرات الحرارية. يعمل بالقواميس عن طريق تثبيط lipases المعدة والبنكرياس ، والانزيمات التي تحلل الدهون الثلاثية في الأمعاء. عندما يتم حظر نشاط الليبيز ، لا تحلم الدهون الثلاثية من النظام الغذائي إلى الأحماض الدهنية الحرة القابلة للامتصاص ، وتفرز غير مهضوم بدلا من ذلك.', NULL, 1, 100.13, '2020-08-30 10:34:25', '2020-08-30 10:34:25'),
(519, 'Paxeladine 40 mg 20 caps -', '  Oxeladin', 'Oxeladin is a cough suppressant. it is a highly potent and effective drug used to treat all types of cough of various etiologies. it is not related to opium or its derivatives, so treatment with oxeladin is free of risk of dependence or addiction. oxeladin has none of the side effects (such as hypnosis, respiratory depression, tolerance, constipation and analgesia) which are present when common antitussives, such as codeine and its derivatives, are used. it may be used at every age, as well as in patients with heart disease, since it has a high level of safety and a great selectivity to act on the bulbar centre of cough.', NULL, 1, 20.00, '2020-08-30 10:34:26', '2020-08-30 10:34:26'),
