(1084, 'Item-n shampoo 60ml -', '  Na laurylether sulfat+cocamidopropylbetain+na cl+guar hydroxypropyltriamonium cl+citric a+na benzoat', 'Phenothrin is a chemical that kills insects (an insecticide). it is a man-made (synthetic) chemical similar to the natural insecticides called pyrethrins. phenothrin is one of a group of insecticides known as pyrethroids. it is also used to control scabies (a disease caused by mites that live on the skin).', NULL, 1, 18.00, '2020-08-30 10:39:32', '2020-08-30 10:39:32'),
