(1474, 'Paxeladine 0.2% 125ml syrup -', '  Oxeladin', 'Oxeladin is a cough suppressant. it is a highly potent and effective drug used to treat all types of cough of various etiologies. it is not related to opium or its derivatives, so treatment with oxeladin is free of risk of dependence or addiction. oxeladin has none of the side effects (such as hypnosis, respiratory depression, tolerance, constipation and analgesia) which are present when common antitussives, such as codeine and its derivatives, are used. it may be used at every age, as well as in patients with heart disease, since it has a high level of safety and a great selectivity to act on the bulbar centre of cough.', NULL, 1, 7.00, '2020-08-30 10:42:44', '2020-08-30 10:42:44'),
(1475, 'Noscapine 15mg/5ml 100ml syrup -', '  Noscapine', 'حول noscapinea benzylisoquinoline قلويد (الأفيون قلويد) ، مضاد للسعال ، مسكن خفيف. آلية العمل من noscapineit بمثابة مضاد السعال عن طريق قمع انتقائي للسعال دون المخدر ، مسكن ، أو الاعتماد على إحداث الخصائص. مؤشرات للسعال noscapine1.spasmodic 2. السعال الجاف 3.tritant 3. التهاب القصبات 4. التهاب 5. الالتهابات الفيروسية من الجهاز التنفسي العلوي 6. السعال الديكي (السعال الديكي)', NULL, 1, 5.50, '2020-08-30 10:42:44', '2020-08-30 10:42:44'),
