(1633, 'Pilesetine spray 30 ml -', ' ', 'A topical treatment for hemorrhoids capable of instantly cleaning & hydrating- neutralizing specifically the pro-inflammatory cytokines- inducing exudation of liquid from the dilated blood vessels so as to reduce their volume & allow them to resume their normal physiology & functions- and reducing pain, irritation, itching & bleeding.posology: topical spray on the external lesions (3-4 sprays 4-5 times/day) or a 0.5-1 ml on internal piles, twice a day.', NULL, 1, 195.00, '2020-08-30 10:43:59', '2020-08-30 10:43:59'),
