(1816, 'Pentasa 1 gm 28 supp -', '  Mesalazine(mesalamine)(5-asa)(5-aminosalicylic acid)', 'About mesalazine5-aminosalicylic acid derivative, anti-inflammatory bowel agent.mechanism of action of mesalazinemesalazine exerts its anti-inflammatory action by inhibiting lipoxygenase enzyme. this will leads to decreased production of pro-inflammatory leukotrienes (ltb4) and 5-hydroxy eicosa tetra enoic acids (hete) in the intestinal wall. it inhibits the production of inflammatory mediators like interleukin-1, tumor necrosis factor-alpha etc. indications for mesalazine1.ulcerative colitis 2.crohn`s disease 3.proctitis and proctosigmoiditis (use only suppositories)', NULL, 1, 378.00, '2020-08-30 10:45:27', '2020-08-30 10:45:27'),
