(2276, 'Efficort 0.1% lipocream 15 gm -', '  Hydrocortisone acetate', 'This medication is used to treat hemorrhoids and itching/swelling in the rectum and anus. it is also used with other medications to treat certain intestinal problems (such as ulcerative colitis of the rectum and other rectal/anal inflammatory conditions). hydrocortisone suppositories help to relieve rectal pain, itching, bloody diarrhea, and bleeding by reducing swelling (inflammation) directly in the rectum and anus. hydrocortisone belongs to a class of drugs called corticosteroids.hydrocortisone acetate rect may interact with the following medicationssevere interactions of hydrocortisone acetate rect:these medications are not usually taken together. immunosuppressives- immunomodulatorssystemic corticosteroids/live vaccinescorticosteroids- corticotropin (acth)/amphotericin bglucocorticoids/aldesleukincorticosteroids/mifepristonecorticosteroids/selected anticholinesterase', NULL, 1, 8.00, '2020-08-30 10:53:25', '2020-08-30 10:53:25'),
