(2347, 'Perfalgan 1g/100ml (100ml) sol.for i.v.vial -', '  Paracetamol(acetaminophen)', 'This medicine is an analgesic (it relieves pain) and an antipyretic (it lowers fever).the 100 ml vial is restricted to adults, adolescents and children weighing more than 33 kg.the 50 ml vial is adapted to term newborn infants, infants, toddlers and children weighing less than 33 kg.it is indicated for the short-term treatment of moderate pain, especially following surgery, and for the short-term treatment of fever.the paracetamol solution is administered in intravenous infusion over 15 minutes.', NULL, 1, 39.75, '2020-08-30 10:53:59', '2020-08-30 10:53:59'),
