(2369, 'B-com i.m./i.v. 6 amp - بي-كوم ٦ أمبولات', '  Vitamin b complex', 'About nicotinamidewater soluble vitamin(b complex- vitamin b3), amide of nicotinic acid.mechanism of action of nicotinamidenicotinamide exerts its action by influencing metabolic reactions. it is converted in to coenzymes ncotinamide adenine dinucleotide (nad) and its phosphate ncotinamide adenine dinucleotide phosphate (nadp) involved in oxidation reduction reactions. these pyridine nucleotides act as hydrogen acceptors in the electron transport chain in tissue respiration, glycolysis, and fat synthesis. nicotinic acid in high doses has vasodilator effects and also improves lipid profile- reduces serum cholesterol, raises hdl level, lowers vldl, and ldl levels.indications for nicotinamide1.pellagra 2.niacin deficiency 3.hartnup disease', NULL, 1, 24.00, '2020-08-30 10:54:10', '2020-08-30 10:54:10'),
(2370, 'Intaxel 6mg/ml 260mg vial -', '  Paclitaxel', 'About paclitaxeltaxane derivative, microtubule inhibitor(mitotic inhibitor), antineoplastic.mechanism of action of paclitaxeldrug binds specifically to the beta- tubuline and then enhances the polymerization of tubuline to stable microtubules. it also interacts directly with microtubules and stabilizing them against depolymerization, inhibits the normal recognition of the microtubule network necessary for mitosis and other cellular functions. drug act at g2/m phase of the cell cycle.indications for paclitaxel1. ovarian cancer 2. breast cancer 3. lung cancer 4. skin cancer 5. cancer of mucous membrane 6. bladder cancer 7. cervical cancer 8. endometrial cancer 9. cancer on abdomen lining 10. fallopian cancer 11. head and neck cancer 12. stomach cancer 13. prostate cancer 14. cancer of testes 15. cancer of unknown primary site', NULL, 1, 1400.00, '2020-08-30 10:54:11', '2020-08-30 10:54:11'),
