(2739, 'Durogesic 12mcg/h trasdermal patches -', '  Fentanyl', 'About fentanyl citratesynthetic primary opioid agonist, anilidopiperidine derivative, narcotic analgesic, general anesthetic.mechanism of action of fentanyl citratethis drug primarily acts on the cns. fentanyl is a pure opioid agonist and primarily acts on the mu opioid receptors located in brain, spinal cord, and in smooth muscles. this action causes alteration of pain perception in patients, thus providing analgesia. it has some hypnotic activity. it causes histamine release rarely.indications for fentanyl citrate1. adjunct to anesthesia 2. induction and maintenance of anesthesia 3. post operative analgesic 4. pre operative analgesic 5. chronic pain interactions for fentanyl citratecns depresants, neuroleptics, narcotic anlgesics, nitrous oxide, conduction anaesthetics.', NULL, 1, 130.00, '2020-08-30 10:57:20', '2020-08-30 10:57:20'),
(2740, 'Rotarix oral vaccine 1.5 ml -', '  Live attenuated rotavirus', 'Rotarix is a vaccine indicated for the prevention of rotavirus gastroenteritis caused by g1 and non-g1 types (g3, g4, and g9) when administered as a 2-dose series. rotarix is approved for use in infants 6 weeks to 24 weeks of age.rotavirus: a virus infection that can cause fever, vomiting, and diarrhea.', NULL, 1, 310.00, '2020-08-30 10:57:21', '2020-08-30 10:57:21'),
(2741, 'Anaflex 10% powder - انافلكس', '  Polynoxylinum', 'دواعي الإستعمال الأمراض الجلدية وحب الشباب والجراحة للأطفال الذين يستخدمون العدوى حول الفم للنساء والتوليد يتم استخدامه لمنع وعلاج التهابات الثدي والشقوق الحلمة للأنف والأذن علاج التهابات الأذن الداخلية والمتوسطة الأذن عن طريق ثقب في طبلة الأذن', NULL, 1, 6.00, '2020-08-30 10:57:21', '2020-08-30 10:57:21'),
(2742, 'Brexin 20mg 10 sachet -', '  Piroxicam', 'About piroxicamnsaid,oxicam derivative, analgesic,antiinflammatory.mechanism of action of piroxicamdrug inhibits the biosynthesis and release of prostaglandins by inhibiting cyclooxygenase enzyme in a reversible manner. in this way it reduces the pg (prostaglandin) concentration in the synovial fluid. it also reduces platelet aggregation (prolong bleeding time), production of igm rheumatoid factor, chemotaxis of leukocytes and ratio of t-helper to t- suppressor lymphocytes.indications for piroxicam1. rheumatoid arthritis 2. osteoarthritis 3. ankylosing spondylitis 4. acute musculo-skeletal disorders 5. acute gout 6. post-operative & post-traumatic pain 7. primary dysmenorrhea interactions for piroxicamanticoagulants: may prolong prothrombin time. beta-blockers: antihypertensive effect may be impaired. cyclosporine: nephrotoxicity of both agents may be increased. lithium: serum lithium levels may be increased. hydantoins: serum hydantoin levels increase', NULL, 1, 29.00, '2020-08-30 10:57:22', '2020-08-30 10:57:22'),
(2743, 'Miconaz 2% powder 20 gm -', '  Miconazole', 'About miconazolean imidazole derivative, broad spectrum antifungal.mechanism of action of miconazolemiconazole is fungicidal or fungistatic depending on the drug concentrations. i t inhibits the conversion of lanosterol to 14 demethyl lanosterol by inhibiting the cytochromep450 enzyme 14 alpha demethylase and impair ergosterol synthesisindications for miconazole1.tinea versicolor 2.vulvovaginal candidiasis 3.tinea pedis 4.tinea corporis 5.tinea cruris 6.otomycosis 7.onychomycosis 8.oral candidiasis 9.intestinal candidiasis 10.diaper dermatitis', NULL, 1, 9.25, '2020-08-30 10:57:22', '2020-08-30 10:57:22'),
(2744, 'Racecarox 10mg/gm sachet -', '  Racecadotril', 'About racecadotrila peripherally acting enkephalinase inhibitor, antidiarrheal. mechanism of action of racecadotrilracecadotril is a dipeptide. it is an enkephalinase inhibitor which prevents the degradation of enkephalins. enkephalins are endogenous opioid which act on delta opioid receptor and reduces the cyclic amp level and produces antidiarrhoeal effect. thus the increased concentration of enkephalins reduces the hyper secretions of water and electrolyte in to the intestinal lumen. racecadotril reduces the incidence of diarrhoea and diarrhoea associated symptoms.indications for racecadotril1. acute symptomatic diarrhoeainteractions for racecadotrilno clinically significant interactions involving interference with drug metabolism have been reported with racecadotril.', NULL, 1, 5.00, '2020-08-30 10:57:23', '2020-08-30 10:57:23'),
