(2778, 'Farcocrom 4% eye drops 10 ml -', '  Sodium cromoglycate', 'About sodium cromoglycatesynthetic chromone derivative, mast cell stabilizer, antiallergic, asthma prophylactic.mechanism of action of sodium cromoglycatethis synthetic chromone derivative has several mechanism of action 1. it is a mast cell stabilizer 2. it inhibit chloride channels and inhibit the exaggerated neuronal reflexes triggered by stimulation of irritant receptors on sensory nerve endings (e.g. exercise-induced asthma) and release of preformed cytokines from several type of inflammatory cells (t-cell, eosinophil) in allergen-induced asthma.3. it inhibit calcium influx of the cell 4.it inhibit the enzyme phosphodiesterase 5. it reduce alpha-adrenoreceptor density 6. it inhibit ig-e dependant secretion of cells other than mast cells.', NULL, 1, 8.00, '2020-08-30 10:57:40', '2020-08-30 10:57:40'),
