(2952, 'Nitazoxin 1.2gm/60ml pd. for oral 60ml susp -', '  Nitazoxanide', 'About nitazoxanidea synthetic nitrothiazolyl-salicylamide derivative, antihelminthics ,in schistosomiasis.mechanism of action of nitazoxanideit excerts its action by blocking anaerobic energy metabolism. the drug interfering with the pyruvate-ferredoxin oxidoreductase enzyme depended electron transfer reaction which is an essential step in anaerobic glucose energy metabolism. indications for nitazoxanide1.helminthiasis 2.giardiasis 3.amoebiasis 4.trichomoniasis 5.fasciolasis 6.cryptosporidiosis interactions for nitazoxanidecaution should be exercised while administering nitazoxanide with drugs which are highly plasma bound.', NULL, 1, 9.50, '2020-08-30 10:58:59', '2020-08-30 10:58:59'),
